summary: A nice, simple GUI for removing ENB files when you no longer want them.
descriptionHtml:
This file does just what it says. You can run it from anywhere, not just the Skyrim directory. Report any bugs and I\'ll fix them. Don\'t forget to endorse!



[color=Green][b]UPDATES:[/b][/color]

   -[b]Version 1.1:[/b] -added some files to delete that I forgot the first time; added \"remove sweetFX\" and \"remove SMAA\" options.

   -[b]Version 2.0:[/b] -added some more options to keep d3d9.dll, or ONLY remove that file; added advanced options (see pictures); added \"help\"

   -[b]Version 2.1:[/b] - added version number to bottom left of the window.

   -[b]Version 2.2 ([color=Green]current[/color]):[/b] - redid directory picking code. Will now ask for directory the first time you start it up, then remember it forever (there is a button if you want to change it after that)
                                                    
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------


[size=16][b]The much anticipated ENB Profile switcher is out! Check it out [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/33319]here.[/url][/b][/size]







[b]This requires .NET FRAMEWORK 4.5  -- You probably already have it.[/b]
author: TenmillionDead
